doctype html
html
  head
    title Roux Meetups - #{pageTitle}
    link(rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous")
    link(rel="stylesheet" href="./css/style.css")
    meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0")
    link(href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:300,400&display=block" rel="stylesheet")
  body
    header
      .jumbotron.d-none.d-sm-block
      nav.navbar.navbar.navbar-expand-md.navbar-dark.bg-dark
        .container
          button.navbar-toggler.collapsed(type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbar-collapse" aria-expanded="false")
            span.sr-only Toggle navigation
            |           â˜°
          a.navbar-brand(href="./index.html") Roux Meetups
          #navbar-collapse.collapse.navbar-collapse
            ul.nav.navbar-nav.ml-auto
              li.nav-item
                a.nav-link(href="./index.html") Home
              li.nav-item.dropdown
                a#navbarDropdown.nav-link.dropdown-toggle(href="./speakers.html" role="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false")
                  | Speakers
                .dropdown-menu(aria-labelledby="navbarDropdown")
                  a.dropdown-item(href="./speakers.html") All Speakers
                  .dropdown-divider
                  a.dropdown-item(href="#") Lorenzo Garcia
                  a.dropdown-item(href="./Hillary_Goldwynn.html") Hilary Goldywynn Post
                  a.dropdown-item(href="#") Riley Rudolph Rewington
              li.nav-item
                a.nav-link(href="./feedback.html") Feedback
    article.speakerslist.jumbotron.d-none.d-sm-block
      .container
        .row
          .col-md.text-center
            h4.speakerslist-title Art in Full Bloom
            .speakerslist-name
              | with
              a(href="#") Lorenzo Garcia
            .speakerslist-info.mt-2
              a(href="#")
                img.speakerslist-img.rounded-circle(src="./images/speakers/Lorenzo_Garcia_tn.jpg" alt="Photo of Lorenzo Garcia")
          .col-md.text-center
            h4.speakerslist-title Deep Sea Wonders
            .speakerslist-name
              | with
              a(href="./Hillary_Goldwynn.html") Hilary Goldywynn Post
            p.speakerslist-info.mt-2
              a(href="./Hillary_Goldwynn.html")
                img.speakerslist-img.rounded-circle(src="./images/speakers/Hillary_Goldwynn_tn.jpg" alt="Photo of Hilary Goldywynn Post")
          .col-md.text-center
            h4.speakerslist-title The Art of Abstract
            .speakerslist-name
              | with
              a(href="#") Riley Rudolph Rewington
            p.speakerslist-info.mt-2
              a(href="#")
                img.speakerslist-img.rounded-circle(src="./images/speakers/Riley_Rewington_tn.jpg" alt="Photo of Riley Rudolph Rewington")
    .container.mt-4
      .row
        .col-md-8
          article.article.maincontent
            h1 Who are we?
            p
              | The Roux Academy gets thousands of submissions every year for artists interesting in participating in the
              | CAC exhibits, and selects approximately 200 distinct pieces of contemporary art for display in their
              | collective exhibit.
              | In addition, 12 individuals are honored as Featured Artists - each being granted his or her own exhibit
              | hall to display entire collections or themed pieces.
            p
              | Each Featured Artist has an opportunity to speak at one of our meetups and share his or her vision,
              | perspective, and techniques with attendees on a more personal level than at our large conference. It is
              | truly an honor to be a
              | CAC Featured Artist and many past students artists who were featured at CAC have gone on to brilliant
              | careers in art.
          article.article.maincontent
            h2.article-title Get Busy!
            p
              | If you want to keep up with what's going on with the group, 
              a(href="http://www.meetup.com/rouxmeet") join our meetup group
              | ,
              a(href="http://www.twitter.com/rouxmeet") follow us on twitter
              | . If you're in FaceBook, you can
              |             also 
              a(href="http://www.facebook.com/rouxmeet") join our FaceBook group
              | .
        aside.col-md-4
          article.sidebar
            h1.sidebar-title Who should come?
            ul.sidebar-body
              li Anybody interested in art and the creative industry
              li Painters, sculptors, photographers and graphic artists
              li
                | Those interested in meeting and making a connection with others in the local art scene.
          article.sidebar
            h1.sidebar-title Artwork on display
            p.sidebar-body
              | While you attend the conference, head over to our gallery where you can check out some
              | of the work from our speakers.
